features: 🥩【Food Grade Material】Our air fryer rack is made of high-quality 304 stainless steel, which is safe, finely polished, durable and easy to clean.
🥩【Compatibility】It is compatible with Ninja DZ201 Foodi 8 Qt / DZ401 Foodi 10 Qt DualZone Air Fryer.
🥩【Easy to Use】The rack is convenient to use. It can be installed easily, and each of the three layers is removable. The rack is convenient to store.
🥩【Upgrade Your Air Fryer】Compared with frying food without the rack, the three layers can load more food, maximize the heating surface of food and prevent food from sticking together.
🥩【Multi-Functional】This Air Fryer Rack has multiple usages. You can make a variety of dehydrated fruits or dehydrated beef jerky with the rack, and you can also use it to grill steaks.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Does The Job
reviews.reviewText: Works well, purchase needs to specify unit is for one basket and buyer needs to order two for two baskets. This is the second one I didn't know I needed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars doesn't help cook food evenly
reviews.reviewText: I tried 2 small pork chops. I thought since they both had air circulating, they would cook more or less evenly. With one 1 chop over the other, only the top one was browned evenly. Even with some oil, still a little hard to clean

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Don’t airfry without it!
reviews.reviewText: The size is perfect for the Ninja Airfryer Dual Zone! I bought two and use them most times when I’m airfrying. Perfect for bacon, fries, tots… anything you need the extra space of layers for! Great Product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Works great in 10 quart ninja foodie air fryer
reviews.reviewText: I bought one for my daughter at Christmas after she got her air fryer last fall. She loved it. I recently bought the same air fryer and immediately bought another rack for myself. It is great for making larger amounts without shaking the food around. Made amazing fish sticks. I look forward making other thing using them.I have issues getting them to nestle together for storage. I should have paid better attention to how they arrived nestled together. I just store them in air fryer basket and it solved my issue.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars It serves its purpose
reviews.reviewText: The rack is very difficult to put together and dismantle. Especially when hot! The bottom cannot be used alone, must have the other racks attached. Most of the food had poor circulation to cook in the air fryer. It's a cool premise, but didn't work as well as anticipated. Single or double layer should be the max.
